Body: Description: We have created various CAP print policies to see if any general user Print any sensitive information , than it should report on EPP console .  The " Print Credit Card Windows " for any general user
What We've Learned Updated: "Advanced printing and MTP scanning" was disabled. After enabling it everything worked correctly.

Next Steps Updated: they will test it on a few more computers and enable it globally since they need to set the policy to block printing.
